Class EntityHome<T extends LocalEntity>

java.lang.Object
  org.redpin.android.db.EntityHome<T>
Type Parameters:
T - entity which implements the interface LocalEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEntityHome<T,java.lang.Long>
Direct Known Subclasses:
LocationHome, MapHome, SpinnerDataHome
public abstract class EntityHome<T extends LocalEntity>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEntityHome<T,java.lang.Long>

Abstract class which provides an partial implementation of all function needed to add, get, update and remove entities to/from database. EntityHomes are used to encapsulate androids ContentProvider

Author:
Pascal Brogle (broglep@student.ethz.ch)
